{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Message execution delay in 5 millisecond steps."}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/nordicmesh\/genericmoveset\/delay"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/GenericMoveSet\/delay"},"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Property","externalID":"s:10NordicMesh14GenericMoveSetV5delays5UInt8VSgvp","title":"delay","fragments":[{"text":"let","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"delay","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"UInt8","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:s5UInt8V"},{"text":"?","kind":"text"}],"modules":[{"name":"NordicMesh"}],"symbolKind":"property","role":"symbol"},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh","doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/GenericMoveSet"]]},"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"let"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"delay"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"UInt8","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:s5UInt8V"},{"text":"?","kind":"text"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The purpose of this field is to synchronize transitions initiated"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"by sending the same message multiple times with a short delay."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"For example, a Node would want to send a Generic On Off Set","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Unacknowledged message to a Group Address. In order to increase","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"changes of successful delivery, such message can be repeated."},